{"tid":1553031,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"是咁的，我又設計左幅香港旗","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:46:22.000Z","uid":282277,"like":18,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6755c7ff57bfd90c2df94dcb7a8b77b21a428cb2","tid":1553031,"uid":282277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"黑底黃條旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYAwVvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYAwVvX.png&h=9b2f3361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計意義：<br />\n1. 自由的光明（黃條）劃破黑夜（黑底）<br />\n2. 獅子山的燈光（上：黑夜、中：燈光、下：晚上的獅子山）照亮香港<br />\n<br />\n設計理由：<br />\n1. 三色旗係法國大革命以經開始用，一直以黎，三色旗都係共和、自由嘅代表。雖然我呢幅旗唔係三色，但最少都係三條呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/三色旗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%89%E8%89%B2%E6%97%97&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4980c8ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/三色旗</a><br />\n2. 可以輕易咁放其他野上去而不失霸氣，例子：<br />\n香港紋章<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAAACKs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAAACKs.png&h=39c87162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴大紋章<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9KE4pA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9KE4pA.png&h=4dcd8c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薄扶林大學紋章<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97typpC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97typpC.png&h=5472b9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命（我知個font樣衰，但我冇平時用開個個font，示意圖咋）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igK2hKF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigK2hKF.png&h=39dae3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 設計簡單，只要係任何黑色嘅野上面（黑衫、黑色嘅牆）畫一條黃條就已經係，可以周街畫<br />\n<br />\n4. 黑、黃兩隻色我地一路以黎都係咁用，夠曬代表性。e.g. 我要真普選旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhtRVwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhtRVwT.jpg&h=4e0f7aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 冇同其他咩國家撞色，唯一撞嘅係Victoria II 入面嘅幻想國家多瑙河聯邦<br />\n<br />\n btw 我上面D圖係用excel同screenshot整嫁咋，唔好直接用，要用自已整，黑黃黑姐"},{"pid":"50734e977ec288b80d70587bb21b87e45c2777d6","tid":1553031,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2d505a11b23da0ebf3722321f47907c0eaaea9","tid":1553031,"uid":93890,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"雖然唔鼓勵飛機post<br />\n但黃條劃破黑夜個idea真係唔錯"},{"pid":"abc34b8f0b0bc8f0da95e6a47a71064460a48502","tid":1553031,"uid":60393,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pWoMFV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pWoMFV.png&h=63e8373a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考呢張 但黑藍調轉呢"},{"pid":"ad4080f2794ff0b85c55426cf41f1c02d8c529dd","tid":1553031,"uid":6741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"覺得幾好"},{"pid":"c3363b65fd72af4156573c56392c3155a29fefbf","tid":1553031,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"Love"},{"pid":"5bae7ed151148d8d11d919340ae21f32697acbeb","tid":1553031,"uid":74435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37be498e44ae46590002d7c1d73f1f74174f9bbd","tid":1553031,"uid":282277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"死，隻黃色好似用得太鮮色添"},{"pid":"a77bc08f65da190691967c16d7e5afcb7da290e8","tid":1553031,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"但感覺太黑？ 可唔可以上下黃 中間黑？"},{"pid":"1c8c990afe3f4f5eb726b581d055724c31868eba","tid":1553031,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"用本民前藍取代黑色"},{"pid":"3f42a2798a13c295d2ed31d5d1da04dbb185089c","tid":1553031,"uid":250737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"又幾型"},{"pid":"3991939d956f0f8775a3b7481a79e2163095798f","tid":1553031,"uid":313778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"🐝🐝"},{"pid":"4799998f422a3790ae25f007f2622c7a85cca53b","tid":1553031,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"Idea ok 但香港旗好似應該係要有舊香港旗隻藍色先啱數"},{"pid":"b8b907b80369a00fc28ab4c130f232539d32c9f0","tid":1553031,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"推，加速討論，有國歌冇國旗，今日有國歌士氣都差好遠"},{"pid":"18e708810979a585edc8746c532fec3d0d5182d5","tid":1553031,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"依個make sense"},{"pid":"384825dafb1c390186ca60507ea1d635ac482092","tid":1553031,"uid":282277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"睇完d comment ，咁又試下改改d 野<br />\n原版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03mW7ja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03mW7ja.png&h=811dee8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃黑調轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aq4hRL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAq4hRL3.png&h=e0ca87be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴哈馬版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ab3eTZs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAb3eTZs.png&h=ad526073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港旗藍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi55gcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi55gcP.png&h=65ac6367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n黑轉本民前藍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLWzTZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLWzTZD.png&h=32a021c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n加logo<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmCCRMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbmCCRMn.png&h=53455720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2024c29db3f7f0f2081a52cc73ba5918e93109e","tid":1553031,"uid":47857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"貼一貼自己份劣作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色和平公義<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色</span>自由民主+前英治歷史<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span>中間 代表香港人因民主公義而抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫色</span>邊包住黃色係尊敬每一位曾經抗爭 甚至因抗爭而犠牲的人士<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9X5g7gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9X5g7gy.png&h=8a7dde16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c240774511d44485a3d982faaa46bead9b9da9b5","tid":1553031,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"咁似霹靂州州旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwmTp94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwmTp94.png&h=c3696051&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"081a3b3a96be22f6c6af9edfde656c9708329083","tid":1553031,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67687249_729932574104080_9020367212153667584_n.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQllhWH-ijmF3dMGEM59oBbzzXYx3_3UumY5mZ8mssg7DmEKViWYj9JyTwo20oR3d8c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=f60167695a861b0b53e9f6b68b8cd93c&amp;oe=5E166480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67687249_729932574104080_9020367212153667584_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQllhWH-ijmF3dMGEM59oBbzzXYx3_3UumY5mZ8mssg7DmEKViWYj9JyTwo20oR3d8c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Df60167695a861b0b53e9f6b68b8cd93c%26